text: Sara Ali Khan Pataudi is an Indian actress who mainly works in Hindi films. Born into Saif Ali Khan and his first wife Amrita Singh's family, she began her career in 2018 with the romantic drama Kedarnath (2016) and the action comedy Simmba (2018), which were commercially successful and the former earned her the Filmfare Award for Best Female Debut.
